scene.message:
Master: Oh my, all of you{nl}
together again.{nl}
Back so soon?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Argh, that woman~!{nl}
She sent us all the way{nl}
back here again!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Did Chisato really{nl}
mean what she said?{nl}
Maybe she's being controlled.{waitkey}{clearbox}That's it! That girl Aki{nl}
must be controlling her!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: There was life in{nl}
Kozai's eyes.{waitkey}{clearbox}At the very least, they{nl}
weren't the eyes of someone{nl}
being controlled.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Why don't we go{nl}
see her once more?{nl}
Then we'll understand{nl}
everything.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Anyway,{nl}
let's go meet her{nl}
one more time.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Let's go see her again.{nl}
Kozai might think{nl}
she went too far, too.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Standing here{nl}
gets us nowhere.{nl}
Only thing to do is{nl}
go see her again.{waitkey}{ret}
